description:
Inspired by a fusion of natural history and science fiction, Organic Art is a beautiful revolution in movement, space and time. The package is based on the hypnotic art of internationally renowned computer artist William Latham, whose recent projects include album covers and videos for techno dance group The Shamen. 

Organic Art contains over 100 3D screen saver scenes that generate in real time, continually creating new mutations for you to discover. Organic Art is also fully interactive, letting you design your own virtual scenes with a unique &amp;#039;Evolutionary Generator&amp;#039;. There are over 400 million combinations to explore!

Organic Art WAS available for Windows 3.1, Windows 95 and Windows NT but works with XP...not sure about Vista
